After working hard for ten years, a Twitter user simply known as @Its_Khaya_ has taken to the micro-blogging site to show off the new home she bought for her mother. Posting a photo of the house online, she wrote: “After 10 years of hard work I’ve managed to buy this house for my mother. I know it’s a small house but it shall be a happy home.” Her kind gesture has been praised by netizens. After 10 years of hard work  I've managed to  buy this 👇🏽 house for my mother. I know it's a small house but it shall be a happy home ❤ pic.twitter.com/Tfov1tCNOb Source